OL,3,CLegionella bacteria found in showers
OL,4,Cof public pool
OL,6,FA Jersey public pool will temporarily
OL,7,Fclose its showers just days after
OL,8,Freopening, following Legionella
OL,9,Fbacteria being detected in the water.
OL,11,FThe swimming baths at Les Quennevais
OL,12,FSports Centre only reopened last week
OL,13,Ffollowing months of refurbishment
OL,14,Fworks.
OL,16,FHowever, routine testing of the
OL,17,Fshowers showed a low count of
OL,18,FLegionella species which often grows
OL,19,Fin stagnant water.
