OL,6,FHowever, it can cause pneumonia-type
OL,7,Fsymptoms, including shortness of
OL,8,Fbreath, high fever, and headaches.
OL,10,FA spokesperson from the Infrastructure
OL,11,FDepartment stated: "The work to
OL,12,Fdisinfect the showers will take place
OL,13,Fout of working hours as soon as
OL,14,Fpossible, then new samples will be
OL,15,Ftaken to ensure the treatment has
OL,16,Fworked.
OL,18,F"We will reopen as soon as the samples
OL,19,Fconfirm it is safe to do so."
